Task is specialized on training with POINTERS

Here , was created a function  "const double * aver(const double * arr , size_t size, double& average);"

It should take an array 'arr' , size of 'arr' , and average by refence.

The function provided , should work in the next way:
The function has to put into 'avarage' the arithmetic average of ALL elements of the array,
AND return the pointer of the element of the array , WHOSE
value is closest to the average.

